      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is absolutely pristine\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it strictly in the garage, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
