    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain is mechanically flawless. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry is factory-perfect, and the chassis remains exceptionally rigid. A turn-key specimen for the purist seeking high-revving, naturally aspirated precision.",
