    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade specimen that defines the term 'mint condition.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain or a winter road. The exterior paint retains a mirror-like depth, having been treated with a multi-stage paint correction and a professional ceramic coating; you will find no stone chips, door dings, or even the slightest swirl marks under direct sunlight. All glass is original and crystal clear, and the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash, wrapped in fresh, premium rubber. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The leather upholstery remains supple with absolutely no creasing or bolster wear, and the factory 'new car' scent persists. Every button, switch, and digital display functions with crisp, tactile precision, and the dashboard is flawless with no UV fading. Mechanically, the car is peerless. It features a full, documented service history from authorized specialists, with a recent major service including all fluid flushes and a comprehensive multi-point inspection that returned a perfect score. The engine bay is detailed to show-quality standards, and the undercarriage is as clean as the topside. This sale includes the original window sticker, two sets of keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a bespoke car cover. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
